#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:2
msgid "Kerberos"
msgstr "Kerberos"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:6
msgid ""
"Kerberos协议起源于美国麻省理工学院Athena项目，基于公私钥加密体制，为分布式环境提供双向验证，在RFC "
"1510中被采纳，Kerberos是Windows域环境中的默认身份验证协议。"
msgstr ""
"The Kerberos protocol originated from MIT's Athena project. Based on a "
"public-key cryptographic system, it provides mutual authentication for "
"distributed environments and was adopted in RFC 1510. Kerberos is the "
"default authentication protocol in Windows domain environments."

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:8
msgid ""
"简单地说，Kerberos提供了一种单点登录 (Single Sign-On, "
"SSO)的方法。考虑这样一个场景，在一个网络中有不同的服务器，比如，打印服务器、邮件服务器和文件服务器。这些服务器都有认证的需求。很自然的，不可能让每个服务器自己实现一套认证系统，而是提供一个中心认证服务器(Authentication"
" Server, AS)供这些服务器使用。这样任何客户端就只需维护一个密码就能登录所有服务器。"
msgstr ""
"In simple terms, Kerberos provides a single sign-on (Single Sign-On, SSO) "
"method. Consider a network with different servers, such as print servers, "
"mail servers, and file servers. These servers all need authentication. "
"Naturally, it is impractical for every server to implement its own "
"authentication system, so a central Authentication Server (AS) is provided "
"for these servers to use. In this way, any client only needs to maintain one "
"password to log in to all servers."

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:10
msgid "Kerberos协议是一个基于票据(Ticket)的系统，在Kerberos系统中至少有三个角色：认证服务器(AS)，客户端(Client)和普通服务器(Server)。"
msgstr ""
"The Kerberos protocol is a ticket-based system. A Kerberos system has at "
"least three roles: the Authentication Server (AS), the Client, and a regular"
" Server."

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:12
msgid "认证服务器对用户进行验证，并发行供用户用来请求会话票据的TGT(票据授予票据)。票据授予服务(TGS)在发行给客户的TGT的基础上，为网络服务发行ST(会话票据)。"
msgstr ""
"The Authentication Server verifies the user and issues a TGT (Ticket "
"Granting Ticket), which the user uses to request session tickets. Based on "
"the TGT issued to the client, the Ticket Granting Service (TGS) issues STs "
"(Session Tickets) for network services."

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:14
msgid "在Kerberos系统中，客户端和服务器都有一个唯一的名字，叫做Principal。同时，客户端和服务器都有自己的密码，并且它们的密码只有自己和认证服务器AS知道。"
msgstr ""
"In a Kerberos system, both clients and servers have a unique name called a "
"Principal. At the same time, clients and servers each have their own "
"passwords, and those passwords are known only to themselves and the "
"Authentication Server AS."

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:17
msgid "基本概念"
msgstr "Basic Concepts"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:18
msgid "Principal(安全个体)"
msgstr "Principal (security entity)"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:19
msgid "被认证的个体，有一个名字(name)和口令(password)"
msgstr "An authenticated entity with a name and password"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:20
msgid "KDC (Key Distribution Center)"
msgstr "KDC (Key Distribution Center)"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:21
msgid "提供ticket和临时的会话密钥的网络服务"
msgstr "A network service that provides tickets and temporary session keys"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:22
msgid "Ticket"
msgstr "Ticket"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:23
msgid ""
"一个记录，用户可以用它来向服务器证明自己的身份，其中包括用户的标识、会话密钥、时间戳，以及其他一些信息。Ticket "
"中的大多数信息都被加密，密钥为服务器的密钥"
msgstr ""
"A record that a user can use to prove their identity to a server. It "
"includes the user's identifier, a session key, a timestamp, and other "
"information. Most information in a Ticket is encrypted with the server's key"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:24 ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:64
#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:75
msgid "Authenticator"
msgstr "Authenticator"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:25
msgid "一个记录，其中包含一些最近产生的信息，产生这些信息需要用到用户和服务器之间共享的会话密钥"
msgstr ""
"A record containing recently generated information, which requires the "
"session key shared between the user and the server"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:26
msgid "Credentials"
msgstr "Credentials"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:27
msgid "一个ticket加上一个秘密的会话密钥"
msgstr "A ticket plus a secret session key"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:28
msgid "Authentication Server (AS)"
msgstr "Authentication Server (AS)"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:29
msgid "通过 long-term key 认证用户"
msgstr "Authenticates users through a long-term key"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:30
msgid "AS 给予用户 ticket granting ticket 和 short-term key"
msgstr "The AS gives the user a ticket granting ticket and a short-term key"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:31
msgid "认证服务"
msgstr "Authentication service"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:32
msgid "Ticket Granting Server (TGS)"
msgstr "Ticket Granting Server (TGS)"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:33
msgid "通过 short-term key 和 Ticket Granting Ticket 认证用户"
msgstr "Authenticates users through a short-term key and a Ticket Granting Ticket"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:34
msgid "TGS 发放 tickets 给用户以访问其他的服务器"
msgstr "The TGS issues tickets to users so they can access other servers"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:35
msgid "授权和访问控制服务"
msgstr "Authorization and access control service"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:38
msgid "简化的认证过程"
msgstr "Simplified Authentication Process"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:39
msgid "客户端向服务器发起请求，请求内容是：客户端的principal，服务器的principal"
msgstr ""
"The client sends a request to the server. The request contains the client's "
"principal and the server's principal"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:40
msgid "AS收到请求之后，随机生成一个密码Kc, s(session key), 并生成以下两个票据返回给客户端"
msgstr ""
"After receiving the request, the AS randomly generates a password Kc, "
"s(session key), and generates the following two tickets to return to the "
"client"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:41
msgid "给客户端的票据，用客户端的密码加密，内容为随机密码，session，server_principal"
msgstr ""
"A ticket for the client, encrypted with the client's password, containing "
"the random password, session, and server_principal"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:42
msgid "给服务器端的票据，用服务器的密码加密，内容为随机密码，session，client_principal"
msgstr ""
"A ticket for the server side, encrypted with the server's password, "
"containing the random password, session, and client_principal"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:43
msgid ""
"客户端拿到了第二步中的两个票据后，首先用自己的密码解开票据，得到Kc、s，然后生成一个Authenticator，其中主要包括当前时间和Ts,c的校验码，并且用SessionKey"
" Kc,s加密。之后客户端将Authenticator和给server的票据同时发给服务器"
msgstr ""
"After obtaining the two tickets from step 2, the client first decrypts its "
"own ticket with its password to obtain Kc,s, then generates an Authenticator"
" that mainly includes the current time and a checksum for Ts,c, and encrypts"
" it with SessionKey Kc,s. The client then sends both the Authenticator and "
"the ticket for the server to the server"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:44
msgid "服务器首先用自己的密码解开票据，拿到SessionKey Kc,s，然后用Kc,s解开Authenticator，并做如下检查"
msgstr ""
"The server first decrypts the ticket with its own password to obtain "
"SessionKey Kc,s, then decrypts the Authenticator with Kc,s and performs the "
"following checks"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:45 ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:68
msgid "检查Authenticator中的时间戳是不是在当前时间上下5分钟以内，并且检查该时间戳是否首次出现。如果该时间戳不是第一次出现，那说明有人截获了之前客户端发送的内容，进行Replay攻击。"
msgstr ""
"Check whether the timestamp in the Authenticator is within 5 minutes of the "
"current time, and check whether this timestamp has appeared for the first "
"time. If the timestamp is not appearing for the first time, it indicates "
"that someone intercepted content previously sent by the client and is "
"performing a replay attack."

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:46 ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:69
msgid "检查checksum是否正确"
msgstr "Check whether the checksum is correct"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:47 ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:70
msgid "如果都正确，客户端就通过了认证"
msgstr "If all checks pass, the client is authenticated"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:48
msgid "服务器段可选择性地给客户端回复一条消息来完成双向认证，内容为用session key加密的时间戳"
msgstr ""
"The server side can optionally reply to the client with a message to "
"complete mutual authentication. The message contains a timestamp encrypted "
"with the session key"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:49 ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:79
msgid "客户端通过解开消息，比较发回的时间戳和自己发送的时间戳是否一致，来验证服务器"
msgstr ""
"The client verifies the server by decrypting the message and comparing "
"whether the returned timestamp matches the timestamp it sent"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:52
msgid "完整的认证过程"
msgstr "Complete Authentication Process"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:53
msgid "上方介绍的流程已经能够完成客户端和服务器的相互认证。但是，比较不方便的是每次认证都需要客户端输入自己的密码。"
msgstr ""
"The process described above can already complete mutual authentication "
"between the client and the server. However, it is inconvenient because the "
"client must enter its password for every authentication."

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:55
msgid ""
"因此在Kerberos系统中，引入了一个新的角色叫做：票据授权服务(TGS - Ticket Granting "
"Service)，它的地位类似于一个普通的服务器，只是它提供的服务是为客户端发放用于和其他服务器认证的票据。"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, a new role is introduced in the Kerberos system: the Ticket "
"Granting Service (TGS). Its position is similar to a regular server, except "
"that the service it provides is issuing tickets that clients use to "
"authenticate with other servers."

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:57
msgid "这样，Kerberos系统中就有四个角色：认证服务器(AS)，客户端(Client)，普通服务器(Server)和票据授权服务(TGS)。这样客户端初次和服务器通信的认证流程分成了以下6个步骤："
msgstr ""
"In this way, the Kerberos system has four roles: the Authentication Server "
"(AS), the Client, a regular Server, and the Ticket Granting Service (TGS). "
"The authentication process for the client's first communication with the "
"server is then divided into the following six steps:"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:59
msgid "客户端向AS发起请求，请求内容是：客户端的principal，票据授权服务器的rincipal"
msgstr ""
"The client sends a request to the AS. The request contains the client's "
"principal and the ticket granting server's principal"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:60
msgid "AS收到请求之后，随机生成一个密码Kc, s(session key), 并生成以下两个票据返回给客户端："
msgstr ""
"After receiving the request, the AS randomly generates a password Kc, "
"s(session key), and generates the following two tickets to return to the "
"client:"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:61
msgid "给客户端的票据，用客户端的密码加密，内容为随机密码，session，tgs_principal"
msgstr ""
"A ticket for the client, encrypted with the client's password, containing "
"the random password, session, and tgs_principal"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:62
msgid "给tgs的票据，用tgs的密码加密，内容为随机密码，session，client_principal"
msgstr ""
"A ticket for the TGS, encrypted with the TGS password, containing the random"
" password, session, and client_principal"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:63
msgid ""
"客户端拿到了第二步中的两个票据后，首先用自己的密码解开票据，得到Kc、s，然后生成一个Authenticator，其中主要包括当前时间和Ts,c的校验码，并且用SessionKey"
" Kc,s加密。之后客户端向tgs发起请求，内容包括:"
msgstr ""
"After obtaining the two tickets from step 2, the client first decrypts its "
"own ticket with its password to obtain Kc,s, then generates an Authenticator"
" that mainly includes the current time and a checksum for Ts,c, and encrypts"
" it with SessionKey Kc,s. The client then sends a request to the TGS with "
"the following contents:"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:65
msgid "给tgs的票据同时发给服务器"
msgstr "The ticket for the TGS is sent to the server at the same time"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:66
msgid "server_principal"
msgstr "server_principal"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:67
msgid "TGS首先用自己的密码解开票据，拿到SessionKey Kc,s，然后用Kc,s解开Authenticator，并做如下检查"
msgstr ""
"The TGS first decrypts the ticket with its own password to obtain "
"SessionKey Kc,s, then decrypts the Authenticator with Kc,s and performs the "
"following checks"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:71
msgid "tgs生成一个session key组装两个票据给客户端"
msgstr "The TGS generates a session key and assembles two tickets for the client"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:72
msgid "用客户端和tgs的session key加密的票据，包含新生成的session key和server_principal"
msgstr ""
"A ticket encrypted with the session key shared by the client and the TGS, "
"containing the newly generated session key and server_principal"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:73
msgid "用服务器的密码加密的票据，包括新生成的session key和client principal"
msgstr ""
"A ticket encrypted with the server's password, including the newly generated"
" session key and client principal"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:74
msgid "客户端收到两个票据后，解开自己的，然后生成一个Authenticator，发请求给服务器，内容包括"
msgstr ""
"After receiving the two tickets, the client decrypts its own ticket, then "
"generates an Authenticator and sends a request to the server with the "
"following contents"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:76
msgid "给服务器的票据"
msgstr "The ticket for the server"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:77
msgid "服务器收到请求后，用自己的密码解开票据，得到session key，然后用session key解开authenticator对可无端进行验证"
msgstr ""
"After receiving the request, the server decrypts the ticket with its own "
"password to obtain the session key, then decrypts the authenticator with the"
" session key to verify the client"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:78
msgid "服务器可以选择返回一个用session key加密的之前的是时间戳来完成双向验证"
msgstr ""
"The server can choose to return the previous timestamp encrypted with the "
"session key to complete mutual authentication"

#: ../../source/auth/kerberos.rst:82
msgid "优缺点"
msgstr "Advantages and Disadvantages"

